	value = sm ?? md ?? lg ?? xl ?? xxl;
```', 'comment_created': datetime.datetime(2022, 7, 25, 9, 31, 52, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), 'commenter': 'personalizedrefrigerator', 'type': 'User'}, {'comment_id': 928665197, 'comment_body': "This might be simpler:
